<item>
            <title>[LU-11400] NOSYNC flag for FLR mirrors</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11400</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For the purpose of having file versions (per-file snapshots) it is useful to have a &lt;tt&gt;NOSYNC&lt;/tt&gt; flag for a component/mirror so that &lt;tt&gt;lfs mirror resync&lt;/tt&gt; does not resync this mirror with the current file data.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would also be useful if the component stored a timestamp (64-bit seconds) that indicates when the version/snapshot was done. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
